Content: Pro traders arent any better at predicting where the market will go than a hobby trader and its not the job. The difference is all in execution Finding lvls protecting profits once available stopping out  adjusting when wrong and consistant loss size control. Focus there

We are working down the targets nicely in #ES_F. 5492 failure had 5474 5455 then 5438 targets and we are a few points shy of 5438 now. Bears control here until a major level recovrs and that level is now 5474 which would trigger back up.  5438 5414 next down if ES wants

Big bidirectional swings in #ES_F continue. 5492 reclaim was long trigger this morning with 5511 5519 5528 targets. We ran to 5528 sold. 5492 failure was then trigger down to 5474 as posted and we are here now.  5455 5438 are below. 5492 must reclaim to trigger back long

The last 2 days have been the most ideal market for lvl to lvl day traders in months. 5492 triggered long this morning. 5511 5519 5528 were targets. We hit 5528 now back to 5492. As posted keep protecting gains  No change 5492 must keep hold weak. Dip 5483 5474 below

As posted the 5492 reclaim would trigger long in #ES_F This is my core edge The Failed Breakdown. Targets were 5511 hit 5519 hit. Now nothing to do all day but just protect profits and let a runner work. Dont go red on the day.  5528 5554 558286 above. 5492 must hold

The 5492 level remains highly actionable in #ES_F. It held 2x yesterday for 40 and 20 point bounces. I posted it had to recover to squeeze today  good follow through  5511 hit 5519 were targets as posted. Protect profits leave runners. 5528 5550 if bulls want. Dip5492

Yesterday 5519  5492 were key supports in #ES_F. We tested 5519 12x before dipping to 5492 which held 2x once for a 40 point bounce  once for 20. It failed overnight  Plan today NFP at 830. 5474support. 5492 must recover to rally to 5511 5519. 5474 fails dip 5455 5438

Trader of 4 years here. Been reading your NL for about a month now. The way you write it and break things down is incredible. Game changer numerous light bulb moments and reading it everyday gives me hope that with lots of practice I can do this the right way. Thanks Adam!

Closing update #ES_F Its been a good session of lvl to lvl ping pong and the 5519 level remains a magnet with 13 tests now. No change 5493support 5519 must recover to resume the leg up. It will be a large squeeze. Newsletter out soon talking triggers tradecompanion.substack.com

Its been a dream market for lvl to lvl day traders in #ES_F around the 5519 magnet tested 12x. 5492 was support earlier as posted. We sold there exactly bounced to 5519 ran to 552833 next target exactly then dipped.  No change 5519 must recover to resume up 5493support

It should be no big shock where we are again in #ES_F Right back at the 5519 ATM Machine level for the 12th test. Levels respecting with extreme precision 5493 was target on the fail of 5519 and we sold to 5493 held back to 5519.  552833 5553 next above. Same supports

Its been a good day for lvl to lvl traders in #ES_F and lvls defending well. 5519 was the ATM Machine and after 11 tests it finally failed. 5493 was sell target as posted and we hit it exact  bounced  Bulls need to recover 5519 to set a bottom. 5493 fails we sell 5482 5463

After an incredible 11 tests in 24hrs the 5519 level finally caved in #ES_F at least for now we likely have not seen the end of it triggering down. 5502 then 5493 were sell targets as posted earlier and 5502 is hit. 5482 below   5519 must recover to trigger major squeeze

Precise technicals today in #ES_F 5519 has been the ATM Machine. Targets off it were 5543 hit 5553 hit 5578 and we got to 5553 2x  rejected. Now testing 5519 for the 11th time since yesterday.  Weaker. No change. Must hold to keep 5553 live. Dip 5502 5493 below

Clean follow through in #ES_F  we got a multitarget hit. 5519 remains the ATM Machine level flushing and recovering 10x in 2 days. Todays targets were 5543 hit 5553 just hit 5578. All bonus now protect gains hold runners.  5566 5578 if ES wants. 5519 must hold

The 5519 level remains an ATM Machine in #ES_F. Its major support as posted  just since yesterday we held it flushedrecovered 10x now. Readers will remember we did this exact same thing at 5519 from June 21st to July 2nd.  No change. Must hold to keep 5543 5553 5578 live.

Yesterday 5519 was key support as posted in #ES_F. I was looking for a rally off it to 5554 calling it an ATM Machine and we held it an incredible 9x yesterday alone  Plan today No change. 5519support weak now. Keeps 5543 5542 5578 level. 19 fails we sell 5502 5492

Closing update #ES_F 5519 has been ATM machine  provoking a 40 point short squeeze this morning  just defending again. 5535 must recover to resume to 5553 5575. Next leg down starts only when 5502 fails. Newsletter out soon talking triggers tomorrow tradecompanion.substack.com

This morning we got a classic short squeeze 1st of this pullback leg. 5519 was support as posted with 5535 5542 5554 targets. We got 5554 in #ES_F then dipped. Now back at 5519 again.  No change 5519support. 5535 must recover to resume up. Next heavy leg down starts5502
